    <learning>
      <learningContent>
        <title>Replacing the Light Bulbs</title>
        <lcInstruction>
          <description>
            <warning>
              <warningAndCautionPara>
								Make sure that the bulb(s) is/are cool before you replace it/them.
							</warningAndCautionPara>
            </warning>
            <caution>
              <warningAndCautionPara>Do not touch the glass of the bulb.</warningAndCautionPara>
            </caution>
            <para>When replacing your bike's light bulbs, be sure to turn the switch to the off position.</para>
            <para>
							Remove the protective glass covering from the light fixture assembly. Remove and discard the used bulb.
						</para>
            <para>Take the new bulb from its packaging, and install it in the light fixture. Reinstall the protective glass covering.</para>
          </description>
        </lcInstruction>
      </learningContent>
    </learning>
